'''Dominique Célidor Simon''' (born 29 July 2000) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] for [[Slovak First Football League]] club [[1. FC Tatran Prešov|Tatran Prešov]]. Born in France, he plays for the [[Haiti national football team|Haiti national team]].

==Club career==
Simon is a product of the youth academies of the French clubs [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]] and [[FCM Aubervilliers|Aubervilliers]]. He made one appearance with Aubervilliers in 2019, before moving to the Spanish club [[SD Navarro CF|Navarro]] in 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sofoot.com/breves/ancien-joueur-daubervilliers-dominique-simon-signe-en-d1-estonienne-estonie-paide-linnameeskond|title=Ancien joueur d’Aubervilliers, Dominique Simon signe en D1 estonienne|date=23 February 2022|website=SOFOOT.com}}</ref> On 23 February 2022, he joined the Estonian [[Meistriliiga]] club [[Paide Linnameeskond|Paide]] on a professional contract, and helped them win the [[2021–22 Estonian Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paidelinnameeskond.ee/tere-tulemast-dominique-simon/|title=Paide Linnameeskond – Tere tulemast, Dominique Simon!}}</ref> On 31 January 2024, he moved to the [[Erovnuli Liga]] club [[FC Dinamo Tbilisi|Dinamo Tbilisi]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sportline.ge/fexburti/11725--23-.html|title=დინამო თბილისმა 23 წლის ფრანგი ნახევარმცველი დაიმატა|website=სპორტის ხაზი}}</ref>

On 18 August 2024, he joined the [[Czech First League]] club [[FK Pardubice|Pardubice]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://soccernet.ee/artikkel/endine-paide-poolkaitsja-siirdus-gruusia-kaudu-tsehhi-korgliigasse|title=Endine Paide poolkaitsja siirdus Gruusia kaudu Tšehhi kõrgliigasse|first=Kris|last=Ilves|date=19 August 2024|website=Soccernet.ee - Jalgpall luubi all!}}</ref> On 22 August 2025, he joined [[1. FC Tatran Prešov|Tatran Prešov]] on a year-long loan in the [[Slovak First Football League]].

==International career==
Born in France, Simon is of Haitian descent.<ref name="auto"/> He was called up to the [[Haiti national football team|Haiti national team]] for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://infotbal.cz/pardubice-opousti-zaloznik-simon-sezonu-stravi-na-hostovani-v-presove/|title=Pardubice opustil záložník Simon. Sezonu stráví na hostování v Prešově » inFotbal.cz|date=22 August 2025}}</ref>

